metadata.title: This week in AI: Brushing off new bubble warnings, Google’s AI comeback and Nvidia’s China threat
metadata.description: This week, volatility took hold of the AI trade as bubble fears continued and Nvidia’s blowout earnings failed to steady the market. Deirdre Bosa has the story.
metadata.author: Jasmine Wu,Deirdre Bosa
